{"tid":1080961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"餐廳唔畀帶野飲合唔合理","createTime":"2019-03-28T03:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T13:35:38.000Z","uid":201694,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"37e113732b1e24f0a8b977bb954fb6126cbf32c0","tid":1080961,"uid":201694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:29:19.000Z","msg":"好多餐廳都唔畀帶野飲<br />\n但佢間野啲野飲又賣貴勁多<br />\n一罐可樂都賣十幾<br />\n唔通客人無選擇其他野飲嘅權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次去食元氣帶咗杯珍珠奶茶入去<br />\n佢唔畀我擺係枱面<br />\n係都要我放喺枱下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得唔畀帶野飲入去合唔合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd2e7db9330dced4c834d5083f7b9b4aa9315d3","tid":1080961,"uid":201694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a52cf494ea61117f8606e1d86cf61d0841b99ec","tid":1080961,"uid":37746,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:32:21.000Z","msg":"個個都咁帶佢仲洗做生意嘅？"},{"pid":"745f72b19253e00d52ec9454dceb519a85dbfc9c","tid":1080961,"uid":76063,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:34:40.000Z","msg":"點會唔合理?<br />\n你唔嫌佢野食貴帶爭鮮入去食?"},{"pid":"3415898288305e522b6e35854c52794b9e7ed295","tid":1080961,"uid":201881,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"咁你想飲自己想要嘅野又食人地嘅食物<br />\n可以考慮外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c450f22d8acefeb9d60eed3d6d9138dbe98ac9a4","tid":1080961,"uid":172297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:19:25.000Z","msg":"邊個叫係咁揚擺枱呀on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你買枝裝飲品放係袋到撚有人理你咩"},{"pid":"4435a97a9829573b39af22157df21c407b051a1a","tid":1080961,"uid":62507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:21:31.000Z","msg":"私人地方，人地想點都唔合理？"},{"pid":"887cff60c69f63e9db68cf52c7f89651b7870533","tid":1080961,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:23:45.000Z","msg":"人地都係打份工, 叫你擺枱底咪算好囉<br />\n當然, 你絕對有選擇既權利, 就係幫襯同唔幫襯<br />\n搞清楚咩叫權利先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a45c43c632b313156230715f4e7b0f36400732","tid":1080961,"uid":100131,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"745f72b19253e00d52ec9454dceb519a85dbfc9c","tid":1080961,"uid":76063,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:34:40.000Z","msg":"點會唔合理?<br />\n你唔嫌佢野食貴帶爭鮮入去食?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:23:51.000Z","msg":"諗起個畫面都好笑.<br />\n樓主拎住個膠袋入元氣, 坐低望一望餐牌, 大驚價錢奇貴. 遂從膠袋中取出兩盒爭鮮壽司, 一杯珍珠奶茶, 放在枱面, 準備享用."},{"pid":"9b565d05dc0f1a32fa596b32fcbac26f67d990e2","tid":1080961,"uid":242724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:25:31.000Z","msg":"人地做生意，你估真係求大家開心，打個和?"},{"pid":"690d36002b17c67af27b3d3f5023042379b83551","tid":1080961,"uid":99086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:26:07.000Z","msg":"唔通比你入去霸佢啲位唔做生意？"},{"pid":"52b88342ad02c647adee5bc7ae0730c4d5009c74","tid":1080961,"uid":13638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"同吉野家帶哂野入去打邊爐有咩分別"},{"pid":"3982122c13df6b823aecfbe237b6789952c69072","tid":1080961,"uid":15483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:28:48.000Z","msg":"佢俾你帶既話佢d 野飲點賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da70310db4ec6169d529e19aec43917a470f6dc0","tid":1080961,"uid":206726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:17:09.000Z","msg":"閪客就係你呢挺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" c